data.description: Welcome to 223 Camp Horne Rd! This 4 bed, 2 bath well-appointed Cape Cod is conveniently located in Avonworth SD, just minutes from I-65, I-79, & I-279. If cooking is your thing, you'll fall in love with the newly remodeled, eat-in kitchen (2019) featuring updated appliances, newer cabinets, quartz countertops & bamboo flooring. The first floor hosts a spacious living room, 2 large bedrooms, & a newly updated bathroom (2021). Upstairs contains 2 additional nicely sized bedrooms & an additional full bath. Original hardwood flooring throughout the house. Plenty of room for your vehicles with an integral garage & an oversized driveway where you can fit up to 4 additional vehicles. Looking for outdoor space? Enjoy the new, rear deck (2023) & large yard with a swing set, set on .96 acres. The basement hosts plenty of storage & the laundry area, as well as garage access. Newer windows throughout (2019), newer roof & gutters (2021). What are you waiting for? This one's a must-see!
